{"tid":1050284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[防契弟？] 對抗外國情蒐 普京要國安單位加強軍事保密","createTime":"2019-03-06T23:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T04:25:32.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"271c620f1f36f3b220dd2499c71d20e021cc05bf","tid":1050284,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T23:22:54.000Z","msg":"對抗外國情蒐 蒲亭要國安單位加強軍事保密<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E6%83%85%E8%92%90-%E8%92%B2%E4%BA%AD%E8%A6%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E4%BF%9D%E5%AF%86-143113343.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%258A%2597%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2583%2585%25E8%2592%2590-%25E8%2592%25B2%25E4%25BA%25AD%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%25BB%258D%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AF%2586-143113343.html&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=9dc57233\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E6%83%85%E8%92%90-%E8%92%B2%E4%BA%AD%E8%A6%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E4%BF%9D%E5%AF%86-143113343.html</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社莫斯科6日綜合外電報導）俄羅斯總統蒲亭今天對聯邦安全局（FSB）高階官員演說時表示，外國情蒐網已加緊在俄國境內的活動，國安單位應提升保護軍事機密的力道，尤其是針對新式武器。<br />\n<br />\n蒲亭（Vladimir Putin）曾在現今俄羅斯聯邦安全局的前身，也就是蘇聯國家安全委員會（KGB）工作，並於1990年代領導聯邦安全局。他今天在演說中指出，外國情蒐和間諜機構已在俄羅斯境內加強活動，刺探政治、經濟、科學和技術機密。<br />\n<br />\n蒲亭聲稱，聯邦安全局去年揭露了共計129名外國間諜，以及465名線民。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，聯邦安全局應特別著力於保護和俄羅斯新武器開發、測試和生產工作有關的資訊。"},{"pid":"575828bfec1ec0280e86ad32303e68294894b1dd","tid":1050284,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T23:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98f70d5dcfa6664009d5ca87109856aad18b03d","tid":1050284,"uid":158888,"like":0,